    <h2>🔥 Vulnerabilities</h2>

    <p>🛡️ <b>Cisco ISE and CCP Flaws Have Public Exploits</b><br>
    Cisco warns of bugs in Identity Services Engine and Configuration Professional with PoC exploits available. Patch promptly.<br>
