    <p>📱 <b>Three Qualcomm Zero-Days Added to CISA KEV</b><br>
    CVE-2025-21479, CVE-2025-21480, and CVE-2025-27038 affect Adreno GPU. Enable unauthorized execution and memory corruption. Patches issued; deadline June 24 for federal agencies.<br>
    🔗 <a href="https://www.cisa.gov/news-events/alerts/2025/06/03/cisa-adds-three-known-exploited-vulnerabilities-catalog" target="_blank">Read more</a></p>
