  <div class="news-item">
    <h2>🕵️ Adversaries & Attacks</h2>

    <p>🪤 <b>GitHub Malware Campaign Targets Hackers and Gamers</b><br>
    Backdoored repos deliver malware via build events. 141 repos link to Sakura RAT, Lumma Stealer, and more.<br>
    🔗 <a href="https://www.bleepingcomputer.com/news/security/hacker-targets-other-hackers-and-gamers-with-backdoored-github-code/" target="_blank">Read more</a></p>

    <p>🎣 <b>Hedera NFT Airdrop Scams Steal Crypto</b><br>
    Unsolicited NFTs link to phishing dApps. Victims tricked into giving up seed phrases. FBI issues warning.<br>
    🔗 <a href="https://www.bleepingcomputer.com/news/security/fbi-warns-of-nft-airdrop-scams-targeting-hedera-hashgraph-wallets/" target="_blank">Read more</a></p>

    <p>👮 <b>Ukrainian Hacker Arrested After $4.5M Crypto Mining Scheme</b><br>
    Exploited 5,000+ accounts since 2018. Used OSINT and VMs. Faces up to 15 years in prison.<br>
    🔗 <a href="https://www.bleepingcomputer.com/news/security/hacker-arrested-for-breaching-5-000-hosting-accounts-to-mine-crypto/" target="_blank">Read more</a></p>

    <p>💳 <b>BidenCash Market Takedown Seizes 145 Domains</b><br>
    $17M in stolen card trade disrupted. Over 15M records sold before FBI and partners shut it down.<br>
    🔗 <a href="https://cyberscoop.com/bidencash-marketplace-domains-seized/" target="_blank">Read more</a></p>

    <p>💎 <b>RubyGems Supply Chain Attack Hijacks Telegram Traffic</b><br>
    Malicious plug-ins exfiltrate messages and bot tokens. Targets Fastlane devs.<br>
    🔗 <a href="https://www.darkreading.com/cyberattacks-data-breaches/attackers-impersonate-ruby-packages-telegram-data" target="_blank">Read more</a></p>

    <p>🎭 <b>Brazilian AI-Generated Scam Uses Fake Journalists</b><br>
    Video promotes court payout hoax. Victims pay fees, give data. No actual compensation issued.<br>
    🔗 <a href="https://www.kaspersky.com/blog/fake-bank-payments/53578/" target="_blank">Read more</a></p>

    <p>📧 <b>Conditional Comment Phishing Targets Czech Bank Users</b><br>
    Outlook shows safe link, others reveal malicious site. Clever HTML trick evades detection.<br>
    🔗 <a href="https://isc.sans.edu/diary/rss/32010" target="_blank">Read more</a></p>

    <p>📬 <b>AS-REP Roasting Still Threatens Active Directory</b><br>
    Exploits no pre-auth on Kerberos accounts. Monitor events 4768, 4625. Enforce strong passwords.<br>
    🔗 <a href="https://www.bleepingcomputer.com/news/security/kerberos-as-rep-roasting-attacks-what-you-need-to-know/" target="_blank">Read more</a></p>

    <p>🧬 <b>Chaos RAT Variant Hits Linux and Windows</b><br>
    Masquerades as network tool. Enables remote control, crontab persistence. Used in mining.<br>
    🔗 <a href="https://thehackernews.com/2025/06/chaos-rat-malware-targets-windows-and.html" target="_blank">Read more</a></p>

    <p>🧨 <b>Play Ransomware Hits 900+ Victims</b><br>
    Exploits SimpleHelp and FortiOS. Uses EDR killers, custom binaries. Targets critical infrastructure globally.<br>
    🔗 <a href="https://www.theregister.com/2025/06/04/play_ransomware_infects_900_victims/" target="_blank">Read more</a></p>
